<refnamediv>
<refname>tinydns-showctl</refname>
<refpurpose>dump a tinydns configuration.</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<cmdsynopsis>
<command>tinydns-showctl</command>
<arg choice='opt' rep='repeat'><replaceable>dir</replaceable></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
<title>Description</title>

<para>
<command>tinydns-showctl</command> outputs a summary of the configuration of one or more particular instances of <citerefentry><refentrytitle>tinydns</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry>. 
It treats each <arg choice='plain'><replaceable>dir</replaceable></arg> argument as a the name of a <citerefentry><refentrytitle>tinydns</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry> service directory.
</para>

</refsection>

